public class BasicParticipant<M,S extends Number>
extends AbstractEntity
implements Participant<M,S>

BasicParticipant - 04.03.12

Represents a participant in a chemical reaction, pairing a coefficient with a molecule. The class is generic allow storage of different molecule and coefficient types. The coefficient should extend a number (i.e. Double or Integer.
